  "markup": "\u003Cp\u003EWe understand that experiencing the loss of a close family member is a difficult time. To support you during such periods, we provide bereavement leave, allowing you necessary time away from work to grieve, attend funeral services, and manage personal affairs. This policy outlines the eligible family members for whom leave may be granted and the duration of such leave. We encourage you to communicate with your manager and the People \u0026amp; Culture Team as soon as possible to arrange for this leave.\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\u0026nbsp;\u003C/p\u003E"
}]]></Value>
